com.netflix.imflibrary.st0429_9

Class MappedFileSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.netflix.imflibrary.st0429_9.MappedFileSet

  • @Immutable
public final class MappedFileSet
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is an immutable implementation of the Mapped File Set concept defined in Section A.1 in Annex A of st0429-9:2014. A MappedFileSet object can only be constructed if the constraints specified in Section A.1 in Annex A of st0429-9:2014 are satisfied
